Require dtkt

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontFamily "IBM Plex Mono"
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1000
Set Height 600

Type `dtkt call ExecuteAction -d '{` Enter@500ms
Type `  "name": "actions/echo",` Enter@500ms
Type `  "input": {` Enter@500ms
Type `    "message": "Hello, World!"` Enter@500ms
Type `  }` Enter@500ms
Type `}'` Enter@500ms

Sleep 5s
